OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for SAT 28 FEB
OL,4,G2000FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GThe Allies launch an ill-fated
OL,6,     Gattack on the German-occupied
OL,7,     Gport of Dieppe, France, where the
OL,8,     GNazis proved to be too strong.
OL,9,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,10,     GAt the Battle of Stalingrad, the
OL,11,     Gbesieged Soviet Red Army turned
OL,12,     Gthe tables on the German Army.
OL,13,G2100FCountdown to War
OL,14,     GOn 1st September 1939, 1.5
OL,15,     Gmillion German soldiers poured
OL,16,     Ginto Poland, beginning the
OL,17,     Gcountdown to the 2nd World War.
OL,18,     GJJ Chalmers and Raksha Dave tell
OL,19,     Gthe dramatic story.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
