OL,4,G2200FCountdown to War
OL,5,     GJJ Chalmers and Raksha Dave
OL,6,     Gexplore 2nd September 1939, as
OL,7,     GGermany's invasion of Poland
OL,8,     Gescalates. RAF recruits deploy,
OL,9,     GLondon hospitals are emptied and
OL,10,     GParliament braces for war.
OL,11,G2300FCountdown to War
OL,12,     GOn 3rd September 1939, Britain
OL,13,     Gdeclared war. After a tense
OL,14,     Gultimatum and false alarm,
OL,15,     GBritish planes saw their first
OL,16,     Gaction and the SS Athenia was
OL,17,     Gtorpedoed, marking the first
OL,18,     Gcasualties.
