OL,4,G0000FWentworth Prison
OL,5,     GGritty drama series set in a
OL,6,     Gwomen's prison in Melbourne.
OL,7,     GWhile Bea is held in the
OL,8,     Gpsychiatric unit, Franky is
OL,9,     Gpushed to reveal her biggest
OL,10,     Gsecret to Bridget.
OL,11,G0105FWentworth Prison
OL,12,     GDrama series. Doreen goes into
OL,13,     Glabour after being attacked. Bea
OL,14,     Glearns the story of Jianna. Vera
OL,15,     Gconfronts Ferguson about the
OL,16,     Griot. Fletch recognises Bea's
OL,17,     Gabductor.
OL,18,G0210FWentworth Prison
OL,19,     GDrama series. After her meltdown,
OL,20,     Ga merciless Ferguson is out for
OL,21,     Gvengeance and Jodie, Doreen, Nash
OL,22,     Gand Bridget are the casualties.
